# Polygon Amoy testnet RPC endpoint (e.g. from Alchemy, Infura, or the public
# https://rpc-amoy.polygon.technology). Needed to deploy/anchor on Amoy.
AMOY_RPC_URL=https://rpc-amoy.polygon.technology

# Private key of a TESTNET-ONLY wallet funded with Amoy MATIC (get some from
